<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ب ا:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَبَاءُ)</span> الَّذِي يُلْبَسُ وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(الْأَقْبِيَةُ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(تَقَبَّى)</span> لَبِسَ <span class="c2">(الْقَبَاءَ)</span> . وَقُبَاءٌ مَمْدُودٌ مَوْضِعٌ بِالْحِجَازِ يُذَكَّرُ وَيُؤَنَّثُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>